cs.PL, cs.LO, cs.SE, cs.FL, cs.LG 

This paper deals with the verified implementation of transformations on functional programs, which is a topic that falls under programming languages (cs.PL) and logic in computer science (cs.LO). The paper also discusses the use of the Abella system for proving properties about the implementations, which is related to software engineering (cs.SE). Additionally, the paper focuses on transformations that analyze binding structure, which is a topic in formal languages and automata theory (cs.FL) and possibly also in computational linguistics (cs.LG).
